OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to using abusive
OL,4,Cbehaviour towards Andrew
OL,6,FA man has pleaded not guilty to using
OL,7,Fthreatening or abusive behaviour
OL,8,Ftowards Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor.
OL,10,FAlex Jenkinson, 39, denying a charge
OL,11,Fof using threatening, abusive or
OL,12,Finsulting words or behaviour with
OL,13,Fintent to cause fear or provoke
OL,14,Funlawful violence.
