OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to using abusive
OL,4,Cbehaviour towards Andrew
OL,6,FHe entered his plea at Westminster
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Friday and is
OL,8,Fexpected to stand trial at the same
OL,9,Fcourt on July 29, when prosecutor
OL,10,FJosephine Jones said it is intended
OL,11,Ffor Andrew to give evidence via a
OL,12,Fvideo-link.
OL,14,FJones told the court there "certainly
OL,15,Fis a suggestion" that Jenkinson had an
OL,16,Finterest in the King's brother,
OL,17,Fadding: "Whether that extends to any
OL,18,Fother members of the royal family I
OL,19,Fdon't think I can say that."
