OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to using abusive
OL,4,Cbehaviour towards Andrew
OL,6,FAndrew was out walking his dogs when
OL,7,Fthe alleged incident happened in
OL,8,FWolferton, close to his Marsh Farm
OL,9,Fproperty, shortly after 7.30pm on
OL,10,FWednesday, the Telegraph reported on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,13,FJenkinson, who gave his address as
OL,14,FDebenham in Suffolk, pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Ffailing to provide a specimen of blood
OL,16,Fwhile in custody on the same day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
