OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778335888
OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to using abusive
OL,4,Cbehaviour towards Andrew
OL,6,FHe was granted conditional bail to not
OL,7,Fgo near several sites linked to the
OL,8,Froyal family: Sandringham, Buckingham
OL,9,FPalace, Balmoral, Windsor and
OL,10,FHighgrove.
OL,12,FHe was also ordered not to try to
OL,13,Fcontact Andrew directly or indirectly,
OL,14,For approach him or enter Norfolk.
OL,16,FLast month, the Crown Prosecution
OL,17,FService said prosecutors were
OL,18,F"providing early investigative advice"
OL,19,Fto the police as they carry out their
OL,20,Finquiries into Andrew's links to
OL,21,FJeffrey Epstein.
