OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to using abusive
OL,4,Cbehaviour towards Andrew
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAndrew was arrested in March on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,13,Foffice over his connections with the
OL,14,Fpaedophile financier. He was later
OL,15,Freleased under investigation.
OL,17,FHe is accused of sharing sensitive
OL,18,Finformation with Epstein while serving
OL,19,Fas the UK's trade envoy.
