OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to using abusive
OL,4,Cbehaviour towards Andrew
OL,6,FThe former duke, who is eighth in line
OL,7,Fto the throne, was detained on his
OL,8,F66th birthday following allegations
OL,9,Fthat he shared reports of official
OL,10,Fvisits to Hong Kong, Vietnam and
OL,11,FSingapore with disgraced financier
OL,12,FEpstein.
OL,14,FHe has vehemently denied any
OL,15,Fwrongdoing over his Epstein links.
OL,17,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,18,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,19,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,20,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
